"That's... a pretty serious symptom," Ishii said.[l][r]
"Hmm, I guess so," I replied vaguely. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
[r] "But even if I go to the hospital, they can't explain the cause." [r]
"Well, that's true..." [l][r]
I was lying on the bed in my room, enjoying the phone call with Ishii, which had become a habit. [l][r]
"Are you okay? Are you sleeping properly? Oh, by the way, the test results are..." [r]
"It's okay." [l][r]
I reply in a bothersome manner, but I can't help but smile a little. It's good that no one can tell on the phone. [l][r]

[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
I feel bad for Ishii, but I find him a little funny when he worries about me. [l][r]
Not that it was because of that, but I would always tell Ishii all about my loneliness, my feelings of guilt, and the physical and mental disorders that probably stemmed from those things. [l][r]
[r]Kanazawa also said, "It's easier to have someone listen to you than to have someone speak to you." [r]
...These are words filled with real feeling. [l][r]
In fact, thanks to that, I feel like I have become a lot more comfortable. Before I met Ishii, I would suddenly be unable to stand or sleep, and it was so hard. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
"That's right, the one we talked about the other day, about going to Nagano." [l][r]
"Oh, what about your parents?"
"It would be good if I could get into college." [l][r]
"Well, I suppose so. I'll need a couple of nights..." [r]
"I wish I could have gone." [l][r]
"You can do it. Taking the exam is a piece of cake for you, right?"
"No, I wanted to go right away.
" [l][r]
"I'm so glad you're looking forward to it." [l][r]
Ishii said with a voice that sounded genuinely happy. What a cute person. [l][r]
It was the same when I was making airplanes.
However, when Ishii is engrossed in something, he becomes so engrossed that he can't see anything else, and it seems like he can't hide his emotions. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]

In other words, Ishii cares about me that much. And about you, too. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[bg  time="1500"  method="crossfade"  storage="sinen.png"  ]
