[r]I'm happy. [l][r]
I don't know how far apart Yuu and I are now, but if Ishii thinks about us together, then we'll be in the same place. [l][r]
Who said, "Thought is faster than light?" [l][r]
Honestly, I think that's just an idealistic idea. But it's true that it makes me happy. [l][r]
I'm sure he will treasure those feelings. [l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

